msgid ""
"ChurnLab is a production-ready Machine Learning application that predicts"
" telecom customer churn. Four models (Logistic Regression, Decision Tree,"
" Random Forest, and XGBoost) were trained, tuned with Optuna, and "
"evaluated on the IBM Telco Customer Churn dataset."
msgstr ""
"ChurnLab is a production-ready Machine Learning application that predicts"
" telecom customer churn. Four models (Logistic Regression, Decision Tree,"
" Random Forest, and XGBoost) were trained, tuned with Optuna, and "
"evaluated on the IBM Telco Customer Churn dataset."

